### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5550/api/v1
@churchId = church-uuid-here
@batchId = batch-uuid-here

### Create a new batch
POST {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/batches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sunday Service - Apr 5, 2026",
  "description": "Offering from main sanctuary"
}

### Batches overview (summary + rows; Gracely-style tabs)
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/batches?filter=all&search=&limit=50&offset=0

### Open batches only (not archived, status open)
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/batches?filter=open

### Archived batches
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/batches?filter=archived

### Deposit batch (credit asset account, then close + archive)
POST {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/batches/{{batchId}}/deposit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": "financial-account-uuid-here"
}

### Archive batch only (no ledger; matches Gracely row “Archive”)
POST {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/batches/{{batchId}}/archive

### Get batch by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/batches/{{batchId}}

### Update batch
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/batches/{{batchId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "closed",
  "archived": true
}

### Delete batch
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/batches/{{batchId}}
